org.apache.poi.hslf.record

Class EscherPlaceholder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ddf.EscherRecord
      • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.EscherPlaceholder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public class EscherPlaceholder
extends EscherRecord
    An atom record that specifies whether a shape is a placeholder shape. The number, position, and type of placeholder shapes are determined by the slide layout as specified in the SlideAtom record.(${t_516bd13be32b44eebf7a666c19db875a})
